body:
Hey guys
So about 3-4 days ago, this guy with the Skype name "thatoneguythatlivesinabox" added me, and sent me a link. He proceeded to ask me if the picture in the link is me, and I was dumb enough to click on it. Shortly after, he told me it was malware. The link doesn't work now; it takes you directly to CloudFlare. It's ironic how he DDoS protects a malicious website.

Our Skype conversation went like this ("Me." is the other guy): 


[8/28/14, 3:53:29 PM] Me.: um
[8/28/14, 3:53:31 PM] Me.: Are you at a computer?
[8/28/14, 4:03:57 PM] JKawesome: yes
[8/28/14, 4:05:14 PM] Me.: Is this you? [link removed]
[8/28/14, 4:29:31 PM] Me.: Hello?
[8/28/14, 4:32:24 PM] JKawesome: who are you?
[8/28/14, 4:32:34 PM] Me.: I want to confirm your identity.
[8/28/14, 4:32:42 PM] Me.: So is that picture you?
[8/28/14, 5:13:30 PM] JKawesome: it won’t load
[8/29/14, 6:32:27 PM] Me.: Yeah, look at the link again.
[8/30/14, 12:25:11 PM] Me.: Alright, JKawesome.
[8/30/14, 12:27:08 PM] JKawesome: ?
[8/30/14, 12:27:16 PM] Me.: Did you notice the link I sent you?
[8/30/14, 12:42:47 PM] JKawesome: It’s not working
[8/30/14, 12:42:54 PM] JKawesome: Who are you?
[8/30/14, 12:56:41 PM] JKawesome: I will delete you as a contact if you don’t tell me who you are
[8/30/14, 12:58:15 PM] Me.: The link is fake.
[8/30/14, 12:58:24 PM] Me.: Look at it, it's gyazo.in.
[8/30/14, 12:58:28 PM] Me.: You aren't going anywhere.
[8/30/14, 12:58:32 PM] JKawesome: Tell me who you are.
[8/30/14, 12:58:39 PM] Me.: You don't need to know that.
[8/30/14, 12:58:48 PM] JKawesome: Yes I do.
[8/30/14, 12:59:06 PM] Me.: You know what that link is?
[8/30/14, 12:59:17 PM] JKawesome: Nope
[8/30/14, 1:00:07 PM] JKawesome: Tell me
[8/30/14, 1:00:50 PM] Me.: Well, why don't you find out?
[8/30/14, 1:00:58 PM] Me.: It's better if you get rid of it, you know.
[8/30/14, 1:01:01 PM] JKawesome: Because it doesn’t work?
[8/30/14, 1:01:11 PM] Me.: The normal link is gyazo.com
[8/30/14, 1:01:52 PM] JKawesome: Not found
[8/30/14, 1:02:02 PM] Me.: The link isn't a picture.
[8/30/14, 1:02:10 PM] JKawesome: Then what is it?
[8/30/14, 1:02:16 PM] Me.: Take a guess.
[8/30/14, 1:02:28 PM] JKawesome: Don’t send me a virus
[8/30/14, 1:02:53 PM] JKawesome: If it is one
[8/30/14, 1:04:26 PM] Me.: You already clicked on it.
[8/30/14, 1:04:35 PM] JKawesome: And?
[8/30/14, 1:04:52 PM] Me.: I'm not elaborating any further.
[8/30/14, 1:05:00 PM] JKawesome: It goes directly to Cloudflare
[8/30/14, 1:05:28 PM] Me.: Oh no, I already disabled the link after you clicked it.
[8/30/14, 1:07:45 PM] JKawesome: I clicked it on my phone.
[8/30/14, 1:08:11 PM] Me.: You also clicked on it on your computer.
[8/30/14, 1:08:25 PM] JKawesome: How would you know that?
[8/30/14, 1:08:32 PM] Me.: I'm not going to answer that.

Oh sh*t that dude...... "ME." is a really good hacker, he made over 200 virus that corrupted a lot of systems (Such as the FBI, somewhere :P)... You are lucky you even survived that. (If you did).
